Kawalongela mweye, mkale na mulembe na wanhu wose, na kaleni wanhu weli na uweru, kwaviya habule munhu yonda yamulole Mndewa.
Kawalongela, muilole munhu yoyose sekeyeze chiya chinhu chochimwing'ha Mulungu, na sekemwize mzizi wa ludumbo da kuwinga muhala da kulawa na kuwavwizila wanhu wengi wezatagusigwa na icho.
Kawalongela, sekeyalawe munhu yoyose yonda yamtendele uzinzi hebu munhu yoyose yoyamtegeleze Mulungu, fana Esau, yoyahololile ndiya dimwe muhala, kaguliza ukulu wake kwa ndiya dimwe.
Maabaho vimuvimanyile, Pilato viyendelele kung'hila chila munhu yoyawasagule nhambiko, mbali kahung'higwa, kwaviya hawamulawile bule kubwela uhasanyi wake, hata viyakalile koleleki yalondelele kwa machozi.
Mbali hamukalile kufosela hanhu hana umulima wodaha kugumigwa na moto. Mng'hali hamukalile mwiisuwe, hamukalile zuwa na hupi na mbeho.
